  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: The controls have been completely destroyed by the Hostile LunaMech.
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: That's unfortunate...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: All the LunaMechs are either destroyed or disabled.
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: That's even more unfortunate...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: The ManaSeal is empty and all the contained Mana is missing.
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Definitely not a good sign...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: All of the Lightguard knights are dead.
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Is there any good news here?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'The Hostile LunaMech had the same white hand marks on it as the
      dead guard with the map at Lightfury Outpost.


      Maybe this is a clue.


      Report
      back to High Priestess Luminessa at the Sun Temple and let her know what has
      transpired.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: I'll report to High Priestess Luminessa now
  prerequisiteConditions: []
